Usage: checkCellForPowerDomainBuffering [-help] -cell <string>
                                        -location_domain <string> {[-driver_term <string>] [-effective_domain <string>]}

-help                          # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>                 # from power domain (string, required)
-driver_term <string>          # to power domain (string, optional)
-effective_domain <string>     # from power domain (string, optional)
-location_domain <string>      # output file (string, required)